  "title": "Counting Days and Numbers",
  "article_text": "On Monday, I felt very thirsty after running for two miles. On Tuesday, I drank three glasses of water. On Wednesday, I ate four apples for lunch. On Thursday, I saw five birds in the tree. I counted six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven, twelve, thirteen, fourteen, fifteen, sixteen, seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, and twenty birds in the park. It was a surprise that so many birds were there. If only I had brought more food, they would have stayed longer. Not only did I see birds, but I also felt happy. It is the fresh air that makes me feel good. I will go again next week.",
